# mvp-*.json and detail plans are each dev's local working files (roadmap/sprints in progress).
# By default they are NOT versioned — only the template (mvp-example.json) and the plans/.gitkeep are.
# After `/project-setup` generates your roadmap, `git add -f` them if you want them committed.
mvp-*.json
!mvp-example.json
plans/*.md
!plans/.gitkeep
